Text::Glob::DWIW

Text::Glob::DWIW implements glob(3) style expansion and also
matching against text. So yet another Text::Glob{::Expand,} like module,
but some unique features does exists.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Text::Glob::DWIW


